### ─── 1. PUBLIC AUTHENTICATION ROUTES ────────────────────────────────────────

### Test 1: Register a Brand New User (Uses fresh email to prevent 409 Conflict)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Aryan Bugalia",
  "email": "aryan.fresh99@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

###

### Test 2: Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "aryan.test2@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123"
}


### ─── 2. PROTECTED PROFILE ROUTES (REQUIRES TOKEN) ───────────────────────────

### Test 3: Get Profile (FAIL TEST - No Token Supplied)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile

###

### Test 4: Get Profile (SUCCESS TEST - Uses @token Variable)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Test 5: Update User Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Aryan Sharma Updated"
}


### ─── 3. ADMIN-ONLY OPERATIONS (RBAC LAYER) ──────────────────────────

### Test 6: Get All Registered Users
# Will return 200 OK if @token belongs to an Admin. Returns 403 Forbidden if regular user.
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Test 7: Get Single User By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Test 8: Change a User's Role (Promote / Demote via API)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Test 9: Delete a User Account as Admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── 4. SECURITY & RATE LIMITER STRESS TEST ────────────────────────────────

### Test 10: Rate Limiter Trigger
# Click "Send Request" on this block 11 times rapidly.
# The 11th click will bypass the controller and slap down a 429 Too Many Requests response.
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "hacker.bot@example.com",
  "password": "bruteforceguessing"
}